These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, argentine
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the australian is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Nationality        | australian   | argentine   |
| Transport   | scooter | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, musical
1. the person watching satire movies is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   |
| Movie-Genre      | musical | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, peach
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, milk
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
2. the person eating peach is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | peach | cabbage |
| Beverage   | sprite   | milk     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, scientist
2 different pets are kept: dog, fish
1. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the videographer##8
2. the videographer is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |
| Job   | scientist | videographer |
| Pet    | dog    | fish |

